{"tid":2228150,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[猫哭老鼠］習總伉儷28小時後 首向確診國家元首致電慰問電","createTime":"2020-10-03T10:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T11:38:49.000Z","uid":239336,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"88f33e49e65d8cdaf5de0ca100b2c210f4cba87a","tid":2228150,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普確診武漢肺炎，各國元首均發電慰問，中國國家主席習近平在特朗普公佈確診後28小時後，終於發慰問電。官媒新華社表示，習近平致電特朗普，稱得悉特朗普伉儷確診後，「我和我夫人彭麗媛謹向你和你夫人表示慰問，祝你們早日康復」。這是習近平首次向確診武漢肺炎的外國國家元首發慰問電。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐美大使崔天凱於香港時間周六（3日）早上9時左右，在Twitter祝願特朗普和夫人梅拉妮婭早日徹底康復，是繼外交部發言人華春瑩後，第二名慰問特朗普的中國代表。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普確診武漢肺炎消息傳出後，印度總理莫迪首先致予慰問，然後是英國首相約翰遜、俄國總統普京，北韓最高領導人金正恩亦已發出慰問，盼望特朗普盡快康復。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201003/JCSVOI2DZNEZTK6OEW2ZZU3LFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201003%2FJCSVOI2DZNEZTK6OEW2ZZU3LFU%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=ea94357b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201003%2FJCSVOI2DZNEZTK6OEW2ZZU3LFU%2F&h=e3872946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201003/JCSVOI2DZNEZTK6OEW2ZZU3LFU/</a>"},{"pid":"ecf4fc4e14e727df6edbe6368f041d0b8d7faa51","tid":2228150,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af7523604f41e879e5204add2b8d0b7fb056c9e","tid":2228150,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6212a6faa1ae9e0d513cb543d13110b0a87626","tid":2228150,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,